Wheeljack-X/Empath::

Jackie paces alongside the others.  "So what's new?"

Empath keeps silent, her feline form pressed against Windlord 
supportively.

---------------

Synergy::

Synergy leads her two companions to the Tripred leader.  "You got any 
troops that aren't loopy, Tyreal?"

---------------

Preds::

Flicker and Phoenix make their way to Perceptor.  "So, who's this 
newcomer?"

Skyblaze reverts to his natural, pure-energy state, and drifts 
aimlessly about the base, while Pumpskin returns to his giggling in 
some forsaken corner.

OOC: I'm serious, by the way.  If I have to do this again, I'm not 
likely to do it at all.
